      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>coconut flakes</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden, then set aside and reserve the pan – this is your <strong>toasted coconut</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
