      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> rice noodles</strong> to a bowl and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Set aside for 12-15 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, drain the <strong>noodles</strong>, reserving a cup of <strong>starchy noodle water</strong> and set aside</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
