    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat the reserved pan with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1682419416637-x200.jpg",
