          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1682419420259-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped basa</strong> and <strong>halved green beans </strong>to the pan</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 4-5 min further or until the fish is cooked through and the green beans are tender</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1682419423928-x200.jpg",
