            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fish is cooked through, add the <strong>drained rice noodles </strong>to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spicy curried basa coconut noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy noodle water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
